{"tid":1148020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有時都幾想死","createTime":"2019-05-10T07:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T16:48:04.000Z","uid":213367,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"remark":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：\n[url]https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline[/url]","replies":[{"pid":"0a4ef170f88449dc2775ae4e8e3b8e62de0a1ea6","tid":1148020,"uid":213367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"其實有時都幾想死<br />\n<br />\n我依家人又廢又要咩冇咩<br />\n<br />\n又冇錢又冇學識<br />\n<br />\n個人又寂寞咁<br />\n<br />\n呢排成日都想打開窗跳落去算尻算"},{"pid":"42aa73b622e0a7ae8805cb7dc01d3f1117dc3822","tid":1148020,"uid":194606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:58:47.000Z","msg":"屌 仲以為係我開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYou are not alone"},{"pid":"d812ab53c4292ac1dd675a8779142eeeb5633256","tid":1148020,"uid":158899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"死啦"},{"pid":"141ce9c1e46d4d00ccba23dd37486d9205b8987a","tid":1148020,"uid":213367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d812ab53c4292ac1dd675a8779142eeeb5633256","tid":1148020,"uid":158899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"死啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"其實等咁耐就係等你呢句"},{"pid":"598005a4ee8acdbb361496365d75d9fc86a4c121","tid":1148020,"uid":65220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"巴打做咩事呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4848597b7c8d9bff9555f78aed37b701551a5d2","tid":1148020,"uid":125648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f77157f3210ea3c8794d20bb18bdef55bc0e557","tid":1148020,"uid":122513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a4ef170f88449dc2775ae4e8e3b8e62de0a1ea6","tid":1148020,"uid":213367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"其實有時都幾想死<br />\n<br />\n我依家人又廢又要咩冇咩<br />\n<br />\n又冇錢又冇學識<br />\n<br />\n個人又寂寞咁<br />\n<br />\n呢排成日都想打開窗跳落去算尻算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"看來你心中盛載著的痛苦，已令你覺得生無可戀。人生之中往往有很多重要的決定，而自殺肯定是人一生中最矛盾、最痛苦，也是最重大的決定。我相信，自殺不是你想選擇的，更不是你唯一的選擇，只不過你所面對的困境和痛苦好像超越了你所能應付的，是嗎？<br />\n<br />\n無論你將會如何打算你的前路，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡，好像氣球裡積存的壓力一樣。你不如停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b409ce93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。那裡有一些與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看（<a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk%2Fmyth_showlist.php%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=3eb9207f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.help4suicide.com.hk/myth_showlist.php）。</a> 你更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"d280b125b5feae386070b0c83876b7f8d771ddb0","tid":1148020,"uid":103783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"[img]<br />\n[/img]"},{"pid":"17fda727bc0cbbcc7e3e058a834f06dab3857e7c","tid":1148020,"uid":103783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/original/000/005/393/IKIFEEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Foriginal%2F000%2F005%2F393%2FIKIFEEL.jpg&h=4d3df101&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c60a08109274c2beab27aee2f82217e2c0f87e59","tid":1148020,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"好憎自己<br />\n樣貌 頭髮 頭型 臉型 眼 眉 鼻 嘴唇 皮膚 神情<br />\n聲音 <br />\n身體 <br />\n思考能力<br />\n所有野<br />\n基本上我就係一個錯誤"},{"pid":"53c15f916f7a8a8928c565373d862e1c69e4c5b2","tid":1148020,"uid":213367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60a08109274c2beab27aee2f82217e2c0f87e59","tid":1148020,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"好憎自己<br />\n樣貌 頭髮 頭型 臉型 眼 眉 鼻 嘴唇 皮膚 神情<br />\n聲音 <br />\n身體 <br />\n思考能力<br />\n所有野<br />\n基本上我就係一個錯誤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"Me too"},{"pid":"69cd3b4fabb81268647c1518b314e130aac76b5c","tid":1148020,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c15f916f7a8a8928c565373d862e1c69e4c5b2","tid":1148020,"uid":213367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60a08109274c2beab27aee2f82217e2c0f87e59","tid":1148020,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"好憎自己<br />\n樣貌 頭髮 頭型 臉型 眼 眉 鼻 嘴唇 皮膚 神情<br />\n聲音 <br />\n身體 <br />\n思考能力<br />\n所有野<br />\n基本上我就係一個錯誤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:02:11.000Z","msg":"Me too"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"點樣可以開心D"},{"pid":"ed9f2b4d842c734de0dd33e25b825df77714e2f4","tid":1148020,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:56:39.000Z","msg":"如果可以安樂死就好"},{"pid":"2c1427e189786ef0c31c2262058f0084ed631882","tid":1148020,"uid":252175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"如果唔怕痛一早自殺左"}]}